rows.name:
If we hadn't come to this place, I could have saved
the people of Superbia... I could have saved Nefer...

rows.label: bf10160150_0050
rows.name:
How will you take
responsibility for this, Rex?

rows.label: bf10160150_0070
rows.name: You must be so pleased with yourself.

rows.label: bf10160150_0080
rows.name: Dragging us all the way to these ruins.

rows.label: bf10160150_0090
rows.name:
And now you've accomplished
what you wanted.
